# Allowlisting gitignore template for GO projects prevents us
# from adding various unwanted local files, such as generated
# files, developer configurations or IDE-specific files etc.
#
# Ignore everything by default
*

# --- Allow git config ---
!/.gitignore

# --- Go source & module files ---
!*.go
!go.mod
!go.sum

# --- Documentation & metadata ---
!README.md
!LICENSE
!ARCHITECTURE.md
!Makefile

# --- API (Swagger is part of source of truth) ---
!api/
!api/**

# --- Project structure (services + internal logic) ---
!cmd/
!cmd/**
!internal/
!internal/**
!migrations/
!migrations/**
migrations/.idea/

# --- Infrastructure / deployment ---
!manifests/
!manifests/**
!docker-compose.yaml
!docker-compose.yml
!.golangci.yml

# --- Allow directory structure markers ---
!.gitkeep

# --- Allow directories themselves (required for allowlist to work properly) ---
!*/
